    <field name="abstract_teim">David Lesser was a member of the Communist Party in the 1930s in New York City. This 468 page memoir focuses on his experiences, 1931-1950, including those relating to the 1937 disappearance of communist Juliet Stuart Poyntz.</field>
    <field name="abstract_ssm">David Lesser was a member of the Communist Party in the 1930s in New York City. This 468 page memoir focuses on his experiences, 1931-1950, including those relating to the 1937 disappearance of communist Juliet Stuart Poyntz.</field>
